    <h1 id="persona-creator-🎭">Persona Creator 🎭</h1>
    <p>A simple avatar creator fueled by imagination! Create your persona using <a href="https://gemini.google.com">Gemini</a> and <a href="https://dicebear.com/">DiceBear</a>!</p>
    <h2 id="features-✨">Features ✨</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>🧑 <b>Persona Creation:</b> Create an entire persona from scratch--or from your inspiration!</li>
        <li>🏷️ <b>Unique Name:</b> Get your own code name!</li>
        <li>🌀 <b>Personality:</b> Mix and combine a variety of personalities!</li>
        <li>🖼️ <b>Avatar:</b> Obtain your own avatar in a style suited to the persona!</li>
        <li>🎨 <b>Style:</b> Stay unique and distinct with your own style including colors, style preferences, and more!</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 id="usage-📑📖">Usage 📑📖</h2>
    <p>You can check out the free website here: <a href="https://kmab5.github.io/">Persona Generator 🎭</a>!</p>
    <p>To install and run locally, clone the repository and run the following command in the root folder.</p>
    <pre><code class="language-bash">npm install</code></pre>
    <p>After installing all the necessary packages, you can run the server and access the generator in your browser at <a href="http://localhost:8214">http://localhost:8214</a>.</p>
    <pre><code class="language-bash">node index.js</code></pre>
    <ul>
        <li>🤖 Automatic Mode: Insert a prompt, kick back and watch as your persona takes shape!</li>
        <li>⚙️ Manual Mode: Take control! Guide the creation as much as you like, choose everything!</li>
    </ul>
